'''諾力'''（Nori）是在[[托爾金|托爾金]]小說《[[哈比人歷險記|哈比人歷險記]]》裡登場的一名角色。

諾力是參與{{le|孤山任務|The Quest of Erebor}}任務的[[索林·橡木盾|索林·橡木盾]]（Thorin Oakenshield）及[[比爾博·巴金斯|比爾博·巴金斯]]（Bilbo Baggins）十二伙伴之一<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.theonering.net/torwp/the-hobbit/characters/nori/|title=Nori|date=2010-11-08|newspaper=TheOneRing.net|accessdate=2018-04-12|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180412150023/http://www.theonering.net/torwp/the-hobbit/characters/nori/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，和另外兩名[[矮人_(中土大陸)|矮人]][[朵力|朵力]]和[[歐力|歐力]]為兄弟關係<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2012319/The-Hobbit-s-dwarves-First-look-Dori-Nori-Ori-Lord-Rings-prequel.html|title=The Hobbit sneak peek: Meet Dori, Nori and Ori from Lord of the Rings prequel|newspaper=Mail Online|accessdate=2018-04-12|archive-date=2015-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121041249/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2012319/The-Hobbit-s-dwarves-First-look-Dori-Nori-Ori-Lord-Rings-prequel.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他戴著紫色[[帽子|帽子]]，會演奏[[長笛|長笛]]，也愛好美食<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.glyphweb.com/arda/n/nori.html|title=Nori|accessdate=2018-04-12|publisher=阿爾達百科全書|language=en-GB|archive-date=2018-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180412212019/http://www.glyphweb.com/arda/n/nori.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

他在慘烈的[[五軍之戰|五軍之戰]]中倖存下來，之後與其他同伴們一起定居[[孤山_(托爾金小說)|孤山]]。諾力在[[愛隆會議|愛隆會議]]與[[魔戒聖戰|魔戒聖戰]]時期依舊健在，並可能於[[河谷鎮之役|河谷鎮之役]]中對抗[[索倫_(魔戒)|索倫]]派來的軍隊。

==改編==
在《[[哈比人電影系列|哈比人電影系列]]》裡，諾力由[[傑德·布拉非|傑德·布拉非]]飾演<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/character/ch0234327/|title=Nori (Character)|accessdate=2018-04-12|publisher=IMDB|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223144256/http://www.imdb.com/character/ch0234327/|archivedate=2016-12-23|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://screenrant.com/hobbit-images-dwarves-nori-ori-dori/|title=New 'Hobbit' Image: The Dwarf Brothers Nori, Ori, & Dori|date=2011-07-07|newspaper=Screen Rant|accessdate=2018-04-12|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180412211738/https://screenrant.com/hobbit-images-dwarves-nori-ori-dori/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20110708/000314.htm|title=《霍比特人1》发新剧照 矮人三兄弟盛装亮相|accessdate=2018-04-12|date=2011-07-08|publisher=腾讯网|archive-date=2018-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180412211756/http://ent.qq.com/a/20110708/000314.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據電影編劇們的設想，諾力擅長於[[竊盜|竊盜]]手法，他在十三名矮人中地位較低<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.theonering.net/torwp/2014/10/08/92961-exclusive-jed-brophy-talks-to-torn-part-two/|title=EXCLUSIVE – Jed Brophy talks to TORn: Part Two|date=2014-10-08|newspaper=TheOneRing.net|accessdate=2018-04-12|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180516120837/http://www.theonering.net/torwp/2014/10/08/92961-exclusive-jed-brophy-talks-to-torn-part-two/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://middleearthnews.com/2015/03/12/exclusive-interview-jed-brophy-part-1/|title=EXCLUSIVE Interview: Jed Brophy, Part 1|accessdate=2018-04-12|date=2015-03-12|publisher=Middle-earth News|archive-date=2018-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180412145657/http://middleearthnews.com/2015/03/12/exclusive-interview-jed-brophy-part-1/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

